_:N8aa870e6f3864f249b28fe9ef99976af <http://schema.org/description> "<p>James Gavin is the Head of MoD Technology Transition, as Deputy Director UKDI</p>\n\n<p>The UKDI exists to explore and to accelerate capabilities into Operational use.</p>\n\n<p>Increasingly projects are ‘Agile By Default’ to deliver early operational advantage. The Directorate works closely with all the Front-line Commands, DSTL and the delivery portfolios within the NAD.</p>\n\n<p>James has served in the military, the civil service and industry before joining the MOD. He is a passionate advocate of delivering Operational Advantage through novel ways of working, particularly though applying Agile &amp; Spiral Development and the use of Industry Mission Partners.</p>\n" .
